Created a torus and modified it to be a precursor for donut

Added imperfections to the torus to get a realistic image

Created the icing layer on the donut and added minor imperfections to it

Used Sculpt mode to add "droplet" of "icing droop" type of structures as frequently seen in donuts

Colored the donut, adjusted the surface and sub-surface properties of the donut for more realism.

Adjusted camera position and lighting.

Explored rendering methods, and how to optimize them by balacing image quality and performance
